Metro FM presenter Lerato Kganyago has hit back at critics. News of her seperation from hubby Thami Ndlala shocked the entertainment fraternity, as they were only married two months ago. This was after Lerato posted a statement on her Instagram, announcing their split. Since social media users have been offering their unsolicited opinions about the possible cause of the star's marital woes. She has assured her fans that nobody will touch anything she owns. Tweeted Lerato: "G. Morning. Ain’t nobody touching ANYTHING I OWN that’s FOR SURE! Easy with the speculation, wish you a day full of positivity."